parameters: "I can teach you about equipment and useful items."
"One-handed weapons include daggers, thin swords, long swords, swords, and maces."
“Long swords, swords, and maces are 3 squares in front of you, and short swords are 2 squares in front of you.
The dagger can attack one space in front of you."
"Weapons with a short range have a high speed when attacking in succession.
And the dagger has a certain probability of getting a critical hit that increases damage.
You can parry and evade enemy attacks."
"Two-handed weapons include two-handed swords, two-handed axes, and two-handed sickles."
"Although you can't equip a shield, it has higher attack power and a wider range than one-handed weapons.
The attack range is 1 square to the left and right and 3 squares to the front and side.
"There are two magic weapons: a one-handed staff and a two-handed staff."
“The attack power is low and the range is only one space in front of you, but the magic power increases.
This is when you do a magic attack.”
"And if you walk a certain number of steps while equipped, your SP will recover.
It won't recover right away, but it's an essential ability when fighting with magic.''
“Long-range weapons include handguns, submachine guns, and submachine guns that can be equipped with shields.
There are assault rifles, sniper rifles, and bows that cannot be equipped with shields."
``All of them can use bullets and arrows to attack from a distance.
Handgun, submachine gun, and bow are 5 squares in front.
Assault rifles are 6 squares, sniper rifles are 10 squares.
"Submachine guns and assault rifles fire many bullets at once, but
Since the power of one shot is low, it is not very effective against opponents with high defense power.''
``On the contrary, sniper rifles cannot fire continuously, but
The power of one shot is very high.”
"If you don't have a weapon equipped, the damage you can deal will be drastically reduced.
This is like a penalty that has nothing to do with your attack power status."
"So even though your attack speed is fast, it's still dangerous to fight with your bare hands."
“In addition to costumes that reflect your appearance, there are shields and armor.”
"Shield is a piece of equipment that can increase your defense power.
However, if you are using a gun, bow, or two-handed weapon, you cannot equip it.''
"Armor can reduce damage to costumes from monster attacks."
``Even if the costume gets torn, it can be repaired using a repair kit, so it's not essential.
If you equip armor, you can reduce the number of repairs.
It would be handy to have to make your adventure go smoothly.”
``Items that are useful to have when going on an adventure are
If you're going to fight monsters, it might be a good idea to have it.''
``A repair kit is an item that allows you to repair costumes.
If your costume is about to break, a mark will appear on the left side of your HP or MP.
It's good to use it before it gets destroyed.''
"A teleportation stone is an item that allows you to return to the city."
"You can't save outside of town, so it doesn't hurt to have it in case of an emergency."

“Next is SP, which is necessary to use skills.
If it runs out, you won't be able to use the skill.''
“And ATK is attack power, and DEF is defense power.
The higher your attack power, the more damage you will inflict on the enemy, and the higher your defense power, the less damage you will receive!
MATK and MDEF are magical versions of this! ”
The higher this is, the faster the attack speed will be when you repeatedly attack.

"When attacked by a monster, in addition to damage to HP,
Damage accumulates on costume equipment as well.”

``If the costume is destroyed, there will be monsters that will launch erotic attacks.''

"When monsters are defeated, they drop items.

“You can only have up to 99 items per type!

"Don't be shy! Come and ask me anytime!"
